Daniel B. Cid <daniel.cid@gmail.com>
v0.4 (2005/10/25):
                   Added support for the rootkit detection on the
                   agents. Added hability of "file sharing" between
                   the server and agents. A lot of fixes, improvements,
                   etc. Ported install scripts/makefiles to work on
                   Solaris 9, MacOS 10 and many other platforms. Added
                   agent information (inside agent-info) directory.
                   Modified files:
